<main id="main-content">
<section class="hero">
<div class="wrap hero-grid">
<div>
<div class="eyebrow">Weekly video podcast · New episodes every Friday</div>
<h1><span class="hero-line">Real love. Real chaos.</span><span class="hero-line accent">Three dudes, one life.</span></h1>
<p class="hero-sub"><strong>A Little Throuple Tea</strong> is a gay throuple podcast hosted by real-life partners William, Caleb and Daniel. We talk honestly about commitment, LGBTQ+ relationships, family, money, travel, queer culture and the beautifully unfiltered reality of building one life as three men in love.</p>
<div class="proof-row">
<span>Real-life committed throuple</span>
<span>Full video on Spotify + YouTube</span>
<span>Weekly since September 2025</span>
<span>Season 2 streaming now</span>
</div>
<div class="cta-row">
<a class="btn primary" href="#listen">Start Listening</a>
<a class="btn" href="/watch/">Watch Episodes</a>
<a class="btn" href="/episodes/">Browse Episodes</a>
</div>
</div>
<div class="hero-art">
<img alt="A Little Throuple Tea podcast artwork featuring William, Caleb and Daniel" fetchpriority="high" height="1200" src="https://d3t3ozftmdmh3i.cloudfront.net/staging/podcast_uploaded_nologo/44265273/44265273-1778344436393-5c56aeb4ad5a.jpg" width="1200"/>
<div class="rank-badge">🏆 Ranked #1 Throuple Podcast by Feedspot in 2026</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<section class="section" id="listen">
<div class="wrap">
<h2 class="section-title">Listen to A Little Throuple Tea</h2>
<p class="section-lede">Choose your favorite podcast app, watch full video episodes or subscribe through the RSS feed. New episodes arrive every Friday.</p>
