<div class="wrap search-cluster">
<div class="giveaway">
<h2>📲 Weekly Signed Book Giveaway</h2>
<p>Turn on Throuple Tea push alerts for a chance to win a signed copy of <strong>Tres Amigos, Una Vida</strong>, plus episode drops, winner announcements and surprise chaos.</p>
<button class="btn primary" id="push-subscribe-btn" type="button">🎁 Turn On Push Alerts to Enter</button><p class="install-help" data-install-help=""></p>
<p class="tiny-note" id="push-help-text">Already joined the email list? Cute. Now turn on push alerts too so you’re entered.</p>
